    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/43d4b7f9cbf4b5d627c7fe5694d0912d.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一起玩。</strong></h2>在游戏中，无论是 VR 玩家还是 PC 玩家，都要照顾好你的朋友。Steam 远程联机游玩功能意味着你也可以让朋友在线加入游戏！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逼真的装弹。</strong></h2>每种武器的操作和装弹都与其现实世界的对应物一样。掌握装弹技巧对于生存来说至关重要！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.poster.avif?t=1753880211\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.webm?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002560/extras/e235ca7bfa2e8e4161c26377c1406615.mp4?t=1753880211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进步。</strong></h2>为玩家提供强大的进度系统，包括：可解锁的枪支、配件、玩家升级等等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战利品。</strong></h2>探索和搜索以寻找战利品、新武器、配件等等！",
